CatDescriptText: Sign posted on top of shelves reads: "Please do not use pen or pencils on indices." Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg. 14 reads: "Index Dockets - Left to right: Edward martin, John Farnan and Walter Bradley, docket clerks, assisting persons who examine index records."
TitMainTitle: Docket clerks Edward Martin, John Farnan and Walter Bradley standing behind counter assisting two men with the "General Judgment Index" at Allegheny County Prothonotary Office
